==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}
# The act of [[recount]]ing or [[relate|relating]] in order the [[particular]]s of some action, [[occurrence]], or affair; a [[narrating]].
# That which is [[narrate]]d or recounted; an orderly [[recital]] of the details and particulars of some [[transaction]] or [[event]], or of a series of transactions or events; a [[story]] or [[narrative]].
# In [[rhetoric]]: that part of an [[oration]] in which the speaker makes his [[statement]] of facts.

